name: Token of Friendship
description:
The Token of Friendship is originaly made to support The Metaverse Community, Because The best thing you can get in this NFT Space is not only experience and some new friends, but also the chance to meet new people who really care about you.

NFT made me able to talk more about what I interested at and also it makes me more happy due the support my friends gave me, so this is me sending my love and supports to the community!
